snippet.title: Nicktoons Basketball PC Gameplay Video Last and penultimate Play Game
snippet.description:
Developer:  ImaginEngine, Digital Eclipse 
Publisher:   ValuSoft 
Release:      2004 - 2005
(Composer: Chris Rezanson)

Nickelodeon Seite:  http://www.nick.de/

English:            http://www.nick.com/

Digital Eclpise Site: http://www.digitaleclipse.com/

Valusoft Cosmi Site: http://www.valusoft.com/

Danke an Nickelodeon, für dieses großartige Spiel und alle die daran gearbeitet haben. :)

Thanks to Nickelodeon, for this great game, and everyone who worked on it. :)
